## bounded-loops

This project uses bounded-loops for gated agent tasks. If a `loop.yaml`
exists in a directory you're working in, prefer bounded-loops MCP tools or
`python3 -m bounded_loops.cli` over ad-hoc shell commands.

Core rule: the gate is the ground truth. Never report success from your own
assessment or from `agent_claimed_done`.

Run order: lint, preview, execute, report exact status. Treat `ERROR`, `HALT`,
`PAUSE`, and `KILLED` as non-success outcomes.
